        "text_epQJ8M": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Cala Falcó, our agricultural system is not based on a single doctrine or fixed methodology. It has evolved through observation, experimentation and a deepening relationship with the land itself. Inspired by regenerative, syntropic, biodynamic and ecological agriculture, we have developed an approach guided by the reality of each season, each plant and each part of the estate.<br/><br/>These are the principles that shape the way we cultivate.</p>",
